 in non combat roles and vastly underrepresented in combat and special forces. Many of them are there for the benefits only. The military is just becoming another welfare institution. Theres still heroes there but overall the institution is not preserving American (white) liberty it is just propping up the abomination of modern MLK AMERICA. \r\n\r\nTheres no point in being an American patriot anymore as sad as that is. I\u2019m pro white now. Any minority who was actually based will understand this and also join the pro-white cause. Being pro-American today is basically just being a naive cuck clinging to a dead idealogy while white people are exterminated.", "author": "STFUmuslimCUCKS", "created": 1783013924565, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "ConfusedAngryArmed", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "After birthright citizenship, it\u2019s time to stop being \u201cpro-American\u201d and just be \u201cpro-white\u201d", "last_comment_created": 1783055282205, "content": "<p>A gay libtard I know told me he was watching The USA vs Bosnia World Cup game. I heard the USA won and was mildly happy about it.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>GO USA DURRRR</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Then I saw a picture of the two rosters. Bosnia is almost entirely white and USA team is almost entirely black.</p>\n<p>Why would I root for a bunch of joggers over based white Slavs? All because of our flag?</p>\n<p>The flag means very little at this point, now that any third world trash can walk right in, plop out a baby and establish their family as \u201cAmerican.\u201d Being American used to mean something profound, now it means nothing.</p>\n<p>The rest of the world is basically united in their hatred of white people and their goal of infiltrating our countries and exterminating us. But I\u2019m supposed to have more allegiance with a beaner and a jogger all because of where there mom decided to vacation when they were born?</p>\n<p>Imagine you want to do something patriotic. How about join the military? Oh look it is filled with minorities who have no real allegiance to true Americanism at all. They worship some bastardized 1960s version of MLK Americanism. They\u2019re vastly overrepresented in non combat roles and vastly underrepresented in combat and special forces. Many of them are there for the benefits only. The military is just becoming another welfare institution. Theres still heroes there but overall the institution is not preserving American (white) liberty it is just propping up the abomination of modern MLK AMERICA.</p>\n<p>Theres no point in being an American patriot anymore as sad as that is. I\u2019m pro white now. Any minority who was actually based will understand this and also join the pro-white cause. Being pro-American today is basically just being a naive cuck clinging to a dead idealogy while white people are exterminated.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 32, "score_up": 131, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2072669996195406122", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ATBlsteV6", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 24, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8710890, "raw_content": "", "author": "IlhansBrother", "created": 1783046948404, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "NotInFormation", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crossp